{"tid":657409,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假博士葛珮帆議辦再接恐嚇信　黏上多隻曱甴屍體","createTime":"2018-05-08T05:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T06:09:55.000Z","uid":6604,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18fe256d31828027cb280e0865a1d323752a5380","tid":657409,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180507/s00001/453dd794b213241761ae5e2e38973d8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180507%2Fs00001%2F453dd794b213241761ae5e2e38973d8c.jpg&h=042288d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自3月及4月兩度接獲死亡恐嚇信後，民建聯假博士葛珮帆在立法會的議員辦事處今日再收到由香港寄出的恐嚇信，信封內黏上多隻曱甴的屍體，被壓扁的曱甴屍體遍佈白色紙上，極為噁心。<br />\n<br />\n拆恐嚇信的女職員被嚇到大聲尖叫跳開，感到十分驚慌，覺得是死亡恐嚇。假博士葛珮帆認為發信者的行為極其幼稚及無聊，該行為已涉觸犯刑事罪行。香港是法治社會，任何人不應以恐嚇他人的方式表達意見，立法會議員及所有公職人員都應該在不被騷擾、毋須驚恐下執行職務，不論任何形式的恐嚇行為均為嚴重罪行，必須予以正視，不能姑息，辦事處的職員已就上述事件報案求助。"},{"pid":"f644c47f31145bed85c8c324bc6741678646f963","tid":657409,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b47f5267446d6dc218de264c87851ad327413e9","tid":657409,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c2427474f2d0f6c8f743dc6b5c1bc7e666bc9d","tid":657409,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"郵政局咁污穢架, 叫人點寄信"},{"pid":"29fdde90d65baf0e389b97bfac83c3f5945c2c5d","tid":657409,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:56:20.000Z","msg":"自編自導?"},{"pid":"62bbcc6f9d0eaab9d39648fad3c8503d21530c37","tid":657409,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲？"}]}